@host = http://localhost:8080
@orgId = 123
@userId = 456

### 조직 목록 조회
GET {{host}}/api/v1/organizations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 새 조직 생성
POST {{host}}/api/v1/organizations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Example Organization",
    "description": "This is an example organization",
    "type": "COMPANY"
}

### 특정 조직 정보 조회
GET {{host}}/api/v1/organizations/{{orgId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 조직 정보 수정
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/organizations/{{orgId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Updated Organization Name",
    "description": "Updated organization description",
    "type": "COMPANY"
}

### 조직 삭제
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/organizations/{{orgId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 멤버 목록 조회
GET {{host}}/api/v1/organizations/{{orgId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 멤버 추가
POST {{host}}/api/v1/organizations/{{orgId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": "{{userId}}",
    "role": "MEMBER"
}

### 멤버 제거
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/organizations/{{orgId}}/members/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 멤버 역할 변경
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/organizations/{{orgId}}/members/{{userId}}/role
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "role": "ADMIN"
}

### 멤버 역할 변경 이력 조회
GET {{host}}/api/v1/organizations/{{orgId}}/members/{{userId}}/history
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}